@startuml TrainingFlow
' ============================================================================
' TaijiFlow AI - Training Flow Diagram
' ============================================================================
' Flow:
' 1. Select
' 2. Start
' 3. Calibration (3s)
' 4. Countdown (3s)
' 5. Training (5m) -> Loop Logic
' 6. Summary
' 7. Reset
' ============================================================================

skinparam defaultFontName "Menlo"
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam handwritten false
skinparam shadow false
skinparam nodesep 0.5
skinparam ranksep 0.5

' Style customization
skinparam rectangle {
    BackgroundColor white
    BorderColor black
    FontSize 14
    FontStyle plain
    Padding 10
}

skinparam note {
    BackgroundColor white
    BorderColor none
    FontSize 13
}

' === Nodes ===

rectangle "เลือกท่า+ระดับ" as Select
rectangle "กด \"เริ่มฝึก\"" as Start

rectangle "Calibration\n(ปรับเทียบ)" as Calib
note right of Calib: ← T-Pose 3 วินาที

rectangle "Countdown\n(นับถอยหลัง)" as Count
note right of Count: ← 3-2-1

rectangle "Training Mode\n(ฝึก+วิเคราะห์)\n\nทุก Frame:\n- Pose Detect\n- Analyze\n- Draw\n- Feedback\n- Score" as Training
note right of Training: ← 5 นาที

rectangle "Summary\n(สรุปผล)" as Summary
note right of Summary: ← แสดงคะแนน

rectangle "Reset" as Reset
note right of Reset: ← กลับหน้าแรก

' === Flow ===

Select -down-> Start
Start -down-> Calib
Calib -down-> Count
Count -down-> Training
Training -down-> Summary
Summary -down-> Reset

@enduml
